§Title: This week in Nushell #213
Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10470] added functionality to evaluate 
``$nu``
 during 
``--ide-check``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10433] optimized aarch64 when able
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10427] added a new command: 
``into value``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10418] allowed the 
``values``
 command to support 
``LazyRecord``
s
anka-213 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10467] improved the parser to prevent cubic time on nested parentheses
, and 
[
fixed exponential parser time on sequence of 
[
[
[
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10439] , and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10434] fixed tilde-expansion for multi-byte unicode chars
Hofer-Julian 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10402] made Nushell changes for the improved history isolation in reedline
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10458] removed dead BSON related tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10449] improved assertions in 
``src/tests.rs``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10431] bumped to 
``0.85.1``
 development version
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10426] pinned reedline to 
``0.24``
 for release
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10425] bumped version for the 
``0.85``
 release
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10403] simplified 
``nu!``
 test macros.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10394] ran clippy in tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10368] split up 
``nu-protocol/src/engine/engine_state.rs``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10355] improved 
``select``
 row perf for large N
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10437] updated the lock file
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10424] added a fix to not overwrite arg's type if it's annotated explicitly
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10399] added a new 
``--abbreviated``
 option to 
``table``
tokatoka 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10376] added 2 fuzzers for nu-path, nu-parser
GPadley 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10089] mapped 
``DirectoryNotFound``
 to 
``FileNotFound``
 for 
``open``
 command (issue #10085)
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10064] removed 
``str replace --string``
 after deprecation
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10453] updated the doc in toolchain.toml describing the update plan
